title: Excel Encoder Agent - MediationZone Documentation 9.4 - InfoZone
text: The Excel Encoder agent receives UDRs, converts them to a bytearray format to be translated into an Excel file, and routes them to the workflow. This section has the following subsections: Excel Encoder Agent Configuration Excel Encoder Agent Input/Output Data and MIM Excel Encoder Agent Events Excel Encoder Agent Transaction Behavior
